    <item>
      <title>[부음] 박찬성 前 국가정보원 이사관 별세 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/12/13/PQYSCAJTYZEF3MKLZNF2YSWD5A/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/12/13/PQYSCAJTYZEF3MKLZNF2YSWD5A/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
